WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:01.020
Previously on the o.c.

00:01.020 --> 00:04.380
- I was with Johnny.
- He went through something.

00:04.410 --> 00:05.680
Something like
I went through.

00:05.740 --> 00:07.700
Even if Marissa
was accused,

00:07.740 --> 00:08.790
she wouldn't
go to jail.

00:08.830 --> 00:10.930
She also wouldn't
be going to college.

00:10.960 --> 00:12.410
- Look,can we talk?
- Yeah,okay.

00:12.450 --> 00:13.790
- But before you say anything...
- I like you.

00:13.820 --> 00:14.680
Ah... boy.

00:14.720 --> 00:17.700
Seth,I think it's obvious
that we are soul mates.

00:17.750 --> 00:19.760
What were you doing
talking to her?

00:19.930 --> 00:22.440
You were just gonna scam me
into throwing a fake charity

00:22.500 --> 00:24.630
and leave me
to pick up the pieces.

00:24.670 --> 00:25.740
You don't have
any friends here.

00:25.780 --> 00:26.810
Wrong.

00:26.860 --> 00:28.290
I have Kirsten,

00:28.340 --> 00:30.390
and I won't do this to her.

